Contributions to our pension and OPEB plans were $1.4 billion and $1.6 billion in 2018 and 2017, respectively. Both years
included a $1.0 billion discretionary contribution to our U.S. pension plans. We expect to make approximately $315 million of
contributions to our pension and OPEB plans in 2019. We believe we have adequate resources to fund both pension and OPEB
plans.
